value.value: Catalysis of the reaction: 7,8-dihydrofolate + ATP + formate = 10-formyldihydrofolate + ADP + H+ + phosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction: formate + ferricytochrome b1 = CO2 + ferrocytochrome b1.
Catalysis of the reaction: formate + NADP+ = CO2 + NADPH.
Catalysis of the reaction: ATP + formate = ADP + formyl phosphate + H+.
Catalysis of the reaction: N-formyl-L-aspartate + H2O = formate + L-aspartate.
Catalysis of the reaction: D-fructose + NADP+ = 5-dehydro-D-fructose + NADPH.
Catalysis of the reaction: a ubiquinone + keto-D-fructose = 5-dehydro-D-fructose + a ubiquinol.
Catalysis of the reaction: D-fructose 6-phosphate + phosphate = acetyl phosphate + D-erythrose 4-phosphate + H2O.
Catalysis of the reaction: (24R,24'R)-fucosterol epoxide = acetaldehyde + desmosterol.
Catalysis of the reaction: (E)-2-(2-furyl)-3-(5-nitro-2-furyl)acrylamide = (Z)-2-(2-furyl)-3-(5-nitro-2-furyl)acrylamide.
Catalysis of the reaction: N5-acyl-L-ornithine ester + H2O = N5-acyl-L-ornithine + an alcohol.

Catalysis of the reaction: histamine + L-glutamate + ATP = N(alpha)-gamma-L-glutamylhistamine + products of ATP breakdown.

Catalysis of the reaction: UDP-galactose + N-acetyl-D-galactosaminyl-(N-acetylneuraminyl)-D-galactosyl-1,4-beta-D-glucosyl-N-acylsphingosine = UDP + D-galactosyl-1,3-beta-N-acetyl-D-galactosaminyl-(N-acetylneuraminyl)-D-galactosyl-D-glucosyl-N-acylsphingosine.

Catalysis of the reaction: geissoschizine + NADP+ = 4,21-dehydrogeissoschizine + H+ + NADPH.
Catalysis of the reaction: acetyl-CoA + gentamicin C(1a) = N(2')-acetylgentamicin C(1a) + CoA + H+. This is acetylation of the 2'-amino group of the 6-deoxy-6-aminoglucose ring.
Catalysis of the reaction: 2,5-dihydroxybenzoate + O2 = 3-maleylpyruvate + H+.
Catalysis of the reaction: 2,5-dihydroxybenzoate + H+ = CO2 + hydroquinone.
Catalysis of the reaction: geraniol + NADP+ = geranial + NADPH.
Catalysis of the reaction: ATP + bicarbonate + geranoyl-CoA = 3-(4-methylpent-3-en-1-yl)pent-2-enedioyl-CoA + ADP + 2 H+ + phosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction: geranyl diphosphate = (2S)-bornyl diphosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction: gibberellin 44 + 2-oxoglutarate + O2 = gibberellin 19 + succinate + CO2.
Catalysis of the reaction: UDP-glucose + gibberellin = UDP + gibberellin 2-O-beta-D-glucoside.
Catalysis of the reaction: D-gluconate = 2-dehydro-3-deoxy-D-gluconate + H2O.
Catalysis of the reaction: D-glucosaminate = 2-dehydro-3-deoxy-D-gluconate + NH3.
